<P>THE Divine Original AND DIGNITY OF Government A&s;&s;erted; AND An Advantageous Pro&s;pect of the RULERS <HI>Mortality</HI> Recommended.</P>
<P>A SERMON Preached before His Excellency the GOVERNOUR, the Honourable COUNCIL, and A&s;&s;embly of the Province of the <HI>Ma&s;&s;achu&s;etts-Bay,</HI> in <HI>New-England, May</HI> 31. 1710. The Day for the Election of Her MAJESTIES Council there.</P>
<P>By EBENEZER PEMBERTON Pa&s;tor of a Church in <HI>Bo&s;ton,</HI> and Fellow of <HI>Harvard College</HI> in <HI>Camb.</HI></P>
<P><HI>BOSTON</HI> in <HI>N E.</HI> Printed by <HI>B Green.</HI> Sold by <HI>Samuel Gerri&s;h</HI> at his Shop in Corn hill. 1710.</P>
</DIV1>
<DIV1 TYPE="license">
