<CLOSER><SIGNED><HI>I&s;aac Addington,</HI> Secr.</SIGNED> <DATELINE>Bo&s;ton, <HI>Prim<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> <DATE><HI>June</HI> 1710.</DATE></DATELINE></CLOSER>
